    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"816344\">Aaron Liu</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/116395-maths/topic/Proof.20in.20Lean.204.20formalization.20of.20circuits/near/529102850\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Do you really need a <code>Fin (a * b)</code>? Can you get by with <code>Fin a × Fin b</code>?</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Wont it be a problem with Fin a x Fin b especially when we have multiple tensor products which would result in the index having type tuple?</p>",
